OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FA man who evaded authorities with his
OL,7,Fthree children in the remote New
OL,8,FZealand countryside for nearly four
OL,9,Fyears was shot and killed by a police
OL,10,Fofficer on Monday, according to local
OL,11,Fpolice.
OL,13,FOne officer was critically injured in
OL,14,Fthe incident, with authorities
OL,15,Fconfirming his injuries were
OL,16,F"survivable."
OL,18,FTom Phillips, who did not have legal
OL,19,Fcustody rights for his children,
OL,20,Fdisappeared with them in 2021.
