OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FOne child was with Phillips at the
OL,7,Ftime of the confrontation, and police
OL,8,Fsearched for hours to find the
OL,9,Fremaining two, with concerns over
OL,10,Ffreezing temperatures as night set in.
OL,12,FAll three children have now been taken
OL,13,Finto custody.
OL,15,FPhillips has not been formally
OL,16,Fidentified, but authorities believe he
OL,17,Fwas the man killed in the
OL,18,Fconfrontation.
