OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FThe children's mother issued a
OL,7,Fstatement to Radio New Zealand on
OL,8,FMonday in which she said she was
OL,9,F"deeply relieved" that the "ordeal"
OL,10,Ffor her children had ended.
OL,12,F"They have been dearly missed every
OL,13,Fday for nearly four years, and we are
OL,14,Flooking forward to welcoming them home
OL,15,Fwith love and care," she said.
