OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FThe disappearance of Tom Phillips and
OL,7,Fhis children in December 2021 proved
OL,8,Fchallenging for investigators, who for
OL,9,Fyears scoured the densely forested
OL,10,Farea where it was believed they were
OL,11,Fhiding.
OL,13,FThe family was not believed to have
OL,14,Fever travelled far from the isolated
OL,15,FNorth Island rural settlement of
OL,16,FMarokopa where they lived, but
OL,17,Fcredible sightings of them were rare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
