OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FPhillips did not have legal custody
OL,7,Frights for his children, now around
OL,8,Fnine, ten and 11 years old, Detective
OL,9,FSenior Sergeant Andrew Saunders told
OL,10,Freporters in 2024.
OL,12,FAuthorities said they had not had
OL,13,Faccess to formal education or
OL,14,Fhealthcare since their disappearance.
OL,16,FLocal authorities always believed that
OL,17,FPhillips had help in concealing his
OL,18,Ffamily, and some residents of the
OL,19,Fisolated rural area expressed support
OL,20,Ffor him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
