OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FA reward of 80,000 New Zealand dollars
OL,7,F(#35,000) was offered for information
OL,8,Fabout the family's whereabouts last
OL,9,FJune, but it was never paid.
OL,11,FDecember 2021 was not the first time
OL,12,FPhillips prompted national news
OL,13,Fheadlines after disappearing with his
OL,14,Fchildren. The family went missing that
OL,15,FSeptember, launching a three-week land
OL,16,Fand sea search after Phillips' truck
OL,17,Fwas found abandoned on a wild beach
OL,18,Fnear where he lived.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
