OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FAuthorities eventually ended the
OL,7,Fsearch, concluding the family might
OL,8,Fhave died, before Phillips and the
OL,9,Fchildren emerged from the dense forest
OL,10,Fwhere he said they had been camping.
OL,11,FHe was charged with wasting police
OL,12,Fresources and was due to appear in
OL,13,Fcourt in January 2022, but weeks
OL,14,Fbefore the scheduled date he and the
OL,15,Fchildren vanished again.
OL,17,FThe police did not immediately launch
OL,18,Fa search because Phillips, who is
OL,19,Fexperienced in the outdoors, had told
OL,20,Ffamily he was taking the children on
OL,21,Fanother trip. He never returned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
