OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FThe search intensified again after
OL,7,Fseveral sightings of Phillips in 2023
OL,8,Fin the same region where he had
OL,9,Fvanished. He was last seen on
OL,10,Fsurveillance video in August this year
OL,11,Fas he robbed a grocery store during
OL,12,Fthe night, accompanied by one of his
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,FWhile one child was with Phillips at
OL,16,Fthe time of the confrontation which
OL,17,Fled to his death, the whereabouts of
OL,18,Fhis other two children was unknown for
OL,19,Fmany hours after the shooting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
