OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FNew Zealand's Acting Deputy Police
OL,7,FCommissioner Jill Rogers said "this
OL,8,Fmust come to a conclusion now" more
OL,9,Fthan 12 hours after the shooting.
OL,11,F"We have children that we believe are
OL,12,Funaccompanied in the bush and it's our
OL,13,Fpriority to locate them this evening,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,FThe child who had been with Phillips
OL,17,Fwas taken into custody on Monday and
OL,18,Fwas cooperating with the authorities,
OL,19,Fallowing them to narrow the search
OL,20,Farea, Rogers said.
