OL,6,FIt wasn't until much later that police
OL,7,Fwere able to locate the remaining two
OL,8,Fchildren, who have now all been taken
OL,9,Finto custody.
OL,11,FThe farm supplies store targeted on
OL,12,FMonday was in a small town in the same
OL,13,Fsprawling farming region of Waikato,
OL,14,Fsouth of Auckland, as the small
OL,15,Fsettlement from where the family
OL,16,Fvanished.
