OL,3,CNew Zealand man on the run with his
OL,4,Cthree children, shot dead by police
OL,6,FOne police officer who was shot during
OL,7,Fthe confrontation with Phillips
OL,8,Fremains in hospital. New Zealand's
OL,9,FActing Deputy Police Commissioner Jill
OL,10,FRogers told reporters the police
OL,11,Fofficer was shot in the head and
OL,12,Fcritically injured during the
OL,13,Fconfrontation with Phillips after he
OL,14,Frobbed an agricultural supplies store
OL,15,Fearly Monday morning.
OL,17,FPolice provided first aid, however the
OL,18,Fgunman died at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
