OL,6,FA second person was detained at the
OL,7,Fscene, where multiple firearms were
OL,8,Frecovered by police.
OL,10,FThe injured officer was airlifted to
OL,11,Fhospital around 4.50am local time.
OL,13,FRogers confirmed the officer was
OL,14,Fundergoing surgery at a hospital. His
OL,15,Finjuries were survivable, Rogers said,
OL,16,Fbut he was shot "multiple times with a
OL,17,Fhigh-powered rifle" and further
OL,18,Fsurgeries were expected.
